{"tid":1481009,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【邊鳩個暴力啲呀】鍾鎮濤再撐警：暴力係冇用","createTime":"2019-08-17T14:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T14:16:11.000Z","uid":175314,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a9acb5e6de4a9cafe2bfac86cfbd8c85dfe17ed8","tid":1481009,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"【曾罵年輕人「九唔搭八」】 鍾鎮濤再撐警：暴力係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/B0WLmj?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2FB0WLmj%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1HPcKSbPy461JM9tWmz6mNY%3D&h=ae8a3ec2\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/B0WLmj?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G509Kfw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG509Kfw.jpg&h=c32468b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾鎮濤（阿B）於6月底曾跟梁家輝及譚詠麟（阿倫）參加撐警集會，阿B當日罵年輕人「九唔搭八」，稱奉公守法是理所當然的事。事後有歌迷將阿B和阿倫的唱片毁掉，以示對他們的言論表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n今日阿B出席「反暴力 救香港」集會，同場還有鄺美雲和張明敏等圈中人，阿B又手持國旗拍照，阿B在台上表示，很高興見到沉默一群出來「反暴力 救香港」，他聲稱「支持警隊」，暴力沒有用，否則學校就不會取消體罰，他認為暴力會令社會有不良後果，甚至「令大家都無得撈」，阿B表示香港是大家土生土長的地方，沒人有權破壞，他希望更多演藝界人士出來。他續說：「無國不會有家。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿B依家係人格破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄺美雲終於出嚟表忠撐警，信佛但偽善<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37affd75fd8682bb815a3d83594ef6df5b47b770","tid":1481009,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"818維園見！所有聽日去嘅人都同我入一入嚟！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<